The paper discusses the use of machine learning for autonomous vehicles, which falls under the category of "Machine Learning" (cs.LG). The paper also mentions the use of onboard sensors and data exchange between vehicles, which suggests the involvement of computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and robotics (cs.RO) in the proposed solution. Additionally, the paper mentions the use of active learning, which is a common technique in neural networks (cs.NE).
